  <section title="Flexlay Editor Download">
    <p>
      There exist two level editors for SuperTux, the built-in one
      that comes with SuperTux and is available via the in-game menu
      (available in 0.1.1 and later) and the external one, which is known
      as <a href="http://pingus.seul.org/~grumbel/flexlay/">Flexlay.</a>
      Flexlay is a seperate project that aims to provide level editing
      capabilities for multiple games.
    </p>

    <p>
      It needs <a href="http://www.clanlib.org">ClanLib-0.7-CVS</a>
      and <a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/guile/guile.html">Guile</a> to compile.
    </p>
